sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Browser
    participant CC as ChatController
    participant CS as ChatServiceImpl
    participant PB as PromptBuilder
    participant OpenAI as OpenAI Embedding API
    participant QS as QdrantSearchService
    participant Qdrant as Qdrant REST :6333
    participant Claude as Anthropic Claude API

    Browser->>CC: POST /api/chat/stream<br/>{ "question": "What are Simon's skills?" }
    CC->>CS: askStream(request, userId)
    CS->>CS: new SseEmitter(60s)

    CS->>OpenAI: embedAll([question])<br/>text-embedding-3-small · ~$0.000001/query
    OpenAI-->>CS: float[1536] query vector

    CS->>QS: search(queryVector, topK=3, minScore=0.3)
    QS->>Qdrant: POST /collections/rag_knowledge/points/search<br/>{ vector, limit:3, with_payload:true, score_threshold:0.3 }
    Qdrant-->>QS: [{ score, payload: { text_segment, fileName, category, docId } }]
    QS-->>CS: List<SearchHit>

    alt No hits above minScore
        CS->>Browser: event:message — "I don't have specific information..."
        CS->>Browser: event:done — [DONE]
    end

    CS->>Browser: event:sources — List<SourceChunk> (JSON)
    note over CS,Browser: Sources sent before LLM reply so UI renders immediately

    CS->>CS: join hit texts → context string
    CS->>PB: build(question, context)
    PB-->>CS: prompt string

    CS->>Claude: streamingGenerate(prompt)<br/>claude-haiku-4-5-20251001 · maxTokens=1024
    note over CS,Claude: Each token triggers onNext()

    loop Per token
        Claude-->>CS: token
        CS->>Browser: event:message — token
    end

    Claude-->>CS: onComplete
    CS->>Browser: event:done — [DONE]
